---
// Hero claro y centrado
---

<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero-content text-center">
      <h1>Simplifica tu trabajo diario</h1>
      <p class="hero-description">La herramienta que necesitas para ser m√°s productivo, sin complicaciones ni curvas de aprendizaje.</p>
      <div class="hero-buttons">
        <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary hero-cta">Empezar ahora</a>
        <div class="hero-trust">
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .hero {
    padding: 4rem 0 5rem;
    background: var(--color-base);
  }

  .hero-content {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .hero h1 {
    font-size: 3rem;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--color-text-dark);
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .hero-description {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  .hero-buttons {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .hero-cta {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    padding: 1.25rem 2.5rem;
    border-radius: var(--radius-small);
    font-weight: 500;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px oklch(55% 0.02 50 / 0.15);
  }

  .hero-cta:hover {
    box-shadow: 0 4px 12px oklch(55% 0.02 50 / 0.25);
  }

  .hero-trust {
    margin-top: 0.5rem;
  }

  .hero-trust small {
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    opacity: 0.9;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  /* Responsive */
  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .hero {
      padding: 3rem 0 4rem;
    }

    .hero h1 {
      font-size: 2.25rem;
    }

    .hero-description {
      font-size: 1.125rem;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
    }

    .hero-cta {
      padding: 1rem 2rem;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .hero-trust small {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
  }
</style>
